this again at the movie theater.

353
00:24:30,234 --> 00:24:31,568
Do you want to go see it?

354
00:24:34,067 --> 00:24:35,868
Yes, let's go and see it.

355
00:24:36,367 --> 00:24:38,201
I really wanted to see that too.

356
00:24:38,334 --> 00:24:40,668
What is it, "Be With You".

357
00:24:40,767 --> 00:24:43,534
I wanted to see it too. Let's go then.

358
00:24:44,567 --> 00:24:47,646
