if you see it in a movie theater.

361
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,634
Let's go see it. We can go.

362
00:24:55,968 --> 00:24:58,268
It's really fine.

363
00:24:58,534 --> 00:25:00,713
It's not fine with me, so let's go.

364
00:25:00,801 --> 00:25:02,435
I just really want to see it.

365
00:25:02,701 --> 00:25:04,834
So, we can really go.

366
00:25:05,667 --> 00:25:06,800
To the movie theater.

367
00:25:25,367 --> 00:25:26,601
Why aren't there any people?

368
