O Sol.

369
00:25:46,234 --> 00:25:49,434
Mr. Jang. You came early.

370
00:25:50,167 --> 00:25:52,768
Oh, I had plans nearby.

371
00:25:53,734 --> 00:25:57,134
Let's go. I already bought the tickets.

372
00:25:59,267 --> 00:26:01,901
How about some popcorn with our movie?

373
00:26:02,033 --> 00:26:03,734
Popcorn? That sounds great.

374
00:26:03,934 --> 00:26:05,134
-Let's go.
-Okay.

375
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:08,233
Dong Hyeon, Yeong Sik, get ready.

376
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:11,045
Hello.

377
00:26:11,133 --> 00:26:12,934
-We'll have a caramel popcorn...
-Yes.

378
00:26:13,434 --> 00:26:14,935
Do you want something to drink?

379
00:26:15,901 --> 00:26:16,968
I'll have anything.

380
00:26:17,934 --> 00:26:20,234
-We'll have coke.
-Okay. It's eight dollars.

381
00:26:21,634 --> 00:26:23,246
It's been so long since
I came to the theater.

382
00:26:23,334 --> 00:26:26,035
Is that so? We can come often from now on.

383
00:26:26,300 --> 00:26:27,667
What the heck...

384
00:26:28,601 --> 00:26:30,579
